{"tid":862374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有上連登，但又視而不見嘅人係咩心態？","createTime":"2018-10-14T18:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T03:04:18.000Z","uid":134093,"like":118,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"560e6a97fea6913b3e4e48b4148b76546c6b8075","tid":862374,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:50:12.000Z","msg":"平時就笑尻child 登，到有認真/政治 post 就視而不見<br />\n屌曬你班人老母，特登 share 幾個重要post 去WhatsApp group ，無人討論不特止，仲視而不見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你班撚樣有搞笑post 就識分享，到政治post就睇唔到，港豬都唔足以形容你班撚樣<br />\n<br />\n咁討厭政治，我勸你地唔好再上連登，呢個地方唔啱你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一諗到呢班人喺背後指手畫腳就嬲到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人少又恥笑，人多又話無用，個個都變做軍師，但事實上一次抗爭都未參與過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我至少有立場，就算咩都爭取唔到都好，都好過你班無立場嘅豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd762741641e206f309676cf8d889534d35f771e","tid":862374,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4f96102ca4d6add0f056ad460eaee839c0f245","tid":862374,"uid":22375,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:55:14.000Z","msg":"正評不解釋"},{"pid":"223ec44c6182e08e1062691e211d2e998a947c99","tid":862374,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-1